data: {"type":"response.output_text.done","content_index":0,"item_id":"msg_035d42c509561158006a0fcac81e60819bb8845b2580c36639","logprobs":[],"output_index":1,"sequence_number":139,"text":"Nice to meet you, Mizzenmast! That’s a fantastic name.\n\nWhat would you like to do today? Here are a few quick ideas, or tell me your own:\n- Write a short bio or profile intro using your name\n- Plan a project or goal (study plan, travel itinerary, etc.)\n- Learn something quick (sailing terms, navigation basics, weather patterns)\n- Get help with writing, coding, or planning\n- Chat about sailing, ships, or maritime history\n- Do a quick nautical trivia or riddle\n\nTell me what you’re in the mood for, or share a bit about your interests and I’ll tailor it."}

